{"text_id":12753,"tokens":["The"," debate"," surrounding"," the"," banning"," of"," cars"," in"," cities"," has"," gained"," significant"," traction"," in"," recent"," years",","," as"," urban"," areas"," around"," the"," world"," grapple"," with"," the"," challenges"," of"," air"," pollution",","," climate"," change",","," and"," increasing"," stress"," levels","."," While"," some"," cities",","," such"," as"," Germany","'","s"," Hamburg",","," Paris",","," and"," Bogota"," have"," taken"," steps"," to"," restrict"," or"," ban"," cars"," in"," certain"," areas",","," others"," remain"," hesitant","."," This"," essay"," will"," explore"," the"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks"," of"," car"," bans"," in"," cities",","," using"," examples"," from"," Germany",","," Paris",","," and"," Bogota",".","\n\n","Air"," pollution"," is"," a"," significant"," challenge"," for"," cities"," around"," the"," world","."," According"," to"," the"," World"," Health"," Organization"," (","WHO","),"," air"," pollution"," causes"," an"," estimated"," ","4",".","2"," million"," premature"," deaths"," worldwide"," each"," year","."," Cars"," are"," a"," major"," contributor"," to"," this"," problem",","," as"," they"," emit"," harmful"," pollutants"," such"," as"," nitrogen"," dioxide"," and"," particulate"," matter","."," By"," banning"," cars",","," cities"," can"," significantly"," reduce"," air"," pollution"," and"," improve"," public"," health","."," In"," Hamburg",","," Germany",","," for"," example",","," the"," city"," has"," implemented"," a"," ban"," on"," older",","," more"," polluting"," diesel"," vehicles"," in"," certain"," areas","."," This"," has"," led"," to"," a"," significant"," reduction"," in"," nitrogen"," dioxide"," levels",","," improving"," air"," quality"," for"," residents",".","\n\n","Ban","ning"," cars"," can"," also"," have"," a"," positive"," impact"," on"," stress"," levels","."," City"," living"," can"," be"," stressful",","," and"," the"," constant"," noise"